{"tid":56334,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解人類咁犯賤","createTime":"2016-12-27T07:13:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T08:41:06.000Z","uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19a20cd96987cf77e6a6ac5d83011c9ed5544206","tid":56334,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:13:09.000Z","msg":"啱啱見到有人戴著條手鏈<br />\n條鏈好似我送俾你嗰條護身符<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n忍唔住係巴士喊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n世界上真係得你一個人可以咁輕易觸動到我既情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins>怎麼不放 早是過往雲煙<br />\n越想遺忘 越是反覆掛牽<br />\n而你在心裡面 要怎麼道別<br />\n說這半句再見 已過了多少年</ins></div>"},{"pid":"8a11befa55777109630c0faf6e57922e37414b04","tid":56334,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T07:13:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b93bb5ac0b8e779cb44c694f43bc180d0bea1f8","tid":56334,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449c63d0443705438f6bfe499e2676bdc80770d6","tid":56334,"uid":44101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T08:41:06.000Z","msg":"加油呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 時間可以沖走一切"}]}